title: NY Regional Single-Family Home Price Jumps 8.4% in August 2024
og:description: OneKey速 MLS reports that the regional single-family closed median sale price was $725,000 in August 2024, marking an 8.4% year-over-year increase from $669,000 in August 2023. While there were fewer transactions, they were higher-value.
